From: Ramesh Mandal <ramesh@6epixels.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 13:23:52 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] chore(repo): fill empty root configs, fix avatar routing
 and background typing

- turbo.json: dev/build/lint/typecheck pipeline (was empty, root scripts failed)
- tsconfig.base.json, .prettierrc, .editorconfig, .nvmrc (Node 22), .env.example
- LICENSE: actual MIT text
- App.tsx: wire AvatarScreen into screen switch (identity -> avatar was falling through to welcome)
- background: use WXT browser global instead of untyped chrome (fixes tsc)
